commit message:
Quick and experimental implementation of Fastbook

This is not final and it needs a better implementation.
Fix formatting and whitespace on manifest.
Fix whitespace/formatting as well as comment style
Fix whitespace/formatting for resource xml files
Get rid of .gitignore file, use your own or global
Create a new WebView to handle facebook stuff
Set fosusable=true on webview to fix keyboard focus mode
Make sure the WebView is initialized
Set the PluginState to ON on the webview
Set wide view port on tablet mode
Re-enable hardwareAcceleration so that video playback works
Activity launch mode set to singleInstance
Update version to 1.1.6. Rewrite coming soon (v1.2)
